Congressional Reports: Committed to the Committee of the Whole House on the State of the Union and ordered to be printed

The Committee on Resources, to whom was referred the bill (H.R. 3147) to provide for the exchange of certain Federal lands in the State of California managed by the Bureau of Land Management for certain non-Federal lands, and for other purposes, having considered the same, report favorably thereon with an amendment and recommend that the bill as amended do pass.
